   avatar, but not for an abstract object devoid of human form. Differences
   in connectivity patterns during the observation of biological versus
   non-biological kinematics were additionally observed. Finally, the
   results additionally suggest that the DMN is coupled more strongly with
   key nodes in the action observation network, namely the STS and the SMA,
